      "content": "that makes sense. i guess i'm just wondering about the big picture. if the transition is basically inevitable because of climate change and stuff, then shouldn't the focus be more on how to make it happen faster rather than worrying about the old coal industry? like, is it even worth trying to protect it at this point?",
